text: Tarinat is the second album of Finnish psytrance-duo Eraser vs Yöjalka. It was released in 2003 by Helsinki-based record label Exogenic Records. ==Track listing== #"Nippy News" – 5:56 #"Tärinät" – 6:22 #"Random Sector" – 6:28 #"Huon Ona" – 5:57 #"Mad John's 12 Euros" – 6:13 #"Minor Discomfort" – 6:31 #"Spank?" – 6:14 #"Paranoid Like a Normal Humanoid" – 5:21 #"Hurstinen Kirkkaus" – 7:11 #"Hullujen Poikien Kerrosteoria" – 6:11 == External links == * Official homepage of Eraser Vs.
